For testing the different robots we propose two platforms:

1) Quality platform:

Our simulator

### Launch the world, the pedestrians, and the robot: ###

> roslaunch pedsim_gazebo_plugin hospital.launch

> roslaunch turtlebot3_gazebo turtlebot3_empty_world.launch
or
> roslaunch blattoidea blattoidea.launch

> roslaunch pedsim_simulator hospital_corridor_and_room.launch

### Launch navigation method ###

> roslaunch turtlebot3_navigation turtlebot3_navigation.launch or roslaunch blattoidea navigation.launch

### Test robot ###

> rosrun testbench test_robot.py (select whether to use move_base/amcl and how many tests)

> rosservice call /init_test_server

2) Metric platform:

SocnavBench
